snippet.title: ONE PUNCH MAN: A HERO NOBODY KNOWS - Lightning Max DLC 2
snippet.description:
A new A-Class Hero has stepped up to defend the city in #OnePunchMan A Hero Nobody Knows! Lightning Max is charging into battle with his fierce electric kicks that will send your opponents flying into the air! 

#LightningMax and Suiryu are both available now for One Punch Man: #AHeroNobodyKnows! https://bandainam.co/OnePunchManPO
